<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-666-994  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 666 994.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>InfoWorld  Sept 18 1989 v11 n38 p74(7).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Product Comparison. (Hardware Review) (a comparison of eight300dpi gray-scale scanners) (evaluation)andM;</TITLE><TEXT><ABSTRACT>A comparison of eight 300dpi gray-scale scanners reveals that TheComplete PC's The Complete Page Scanner for $899 is the best valueamong the others, a top performer with quick scan times andimpressive-looking output.andP;  But the scanner has a limited warrantyperiod, and it handles only one page at a time.andP;  Ricoh Corp'sRicoh RS320 for $1,499, is the fastest scanner, with a removabletop for scanning books or oversized materials.andP;  Manuals arewell-written, but trouble-shooting information is missing.andP;  AbatonTechnology Corp's Abaton Scan 300/GS at $2,190 is a sturdyscanner, flatbed, 8-bit, 8.25-by-14 inch maximum scanning area.andO;Abaton Scan is incompatible with built-in VGA on Compaq Deskpro386/20e.andP;  Chinon America Inc's Chinon DS-3000, listed at $895 or$745 without software, is the lowest price among the scanners, andcan scan three-dimensional objects.andP;  Chinon is also the slowest ofthe scanners, and has unclear documentation.andP;  Hewlett-Packard Co'sScanjet Plus for $2,190 ties for top gray levels, and is among thebest in documentation and setup.andP;  Scanjet can be slow to scanphotos.andP;  Microtek's MSF-300G flatbed scanner, for $2,195, alsoties for top gray levels, and has fine workmanship.andP;  The hardwaremanual lacks an index, glossary and instructions in detail.andO;Pentax Teknologies' SB-A4301, priced at $1,525, has fast scantimes and produces top newsprint output.andP;  The SB-A4301 is easy toset up, and has good support policies.andP;  Xerox Imaging SystemsInc's Datacopy 730GS, priced at $1,995, has top color andblack-and-white photo output, and is a fine performer.andP;  However,the default setup conflicts with Compaq 386/20e.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Abaton Technology Corp. (products)Chinon America Inc. (products)Complete PC Inc. (products)Hewlett-Packard Co. (products)Microtek Lab Inc. (products)Pentax Teknologies Corp. (products)Ricoh Corp. (products)Xerox Imaging Systems Inc. (products).andO;Ticker:    HWP; XRX.andO;Product:   Abaton 300/GS (Scanning device)Chinon America DS-3000 (Scanning device)Complete PC Complete Page Scanner (Scanning device)HP ScanJet Plus (Scanning device)Microtek Lab MSF-300G (Scanning device)Pentax Teknologies SB-A4301 (Scanning device)Ricoh RS320 (Scanning device)Xerox Imaging Systems Datacopy 730GS (Scanning device).andO;Topic:     ScanningPeripheralsImaging TechnologyEvaluation.andO;Feature:   illustrationgraphtable.andO;Caption:   Benchmarks: PC image scanners. (graph)Report card: PC image scanners. (table)andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>